#include<iostream>

using namespace std;

struct rectangle
{
	int x1;
	int y1;
	int x2;
	int y2;
};

int main()
{
rectangle r1,r2,r;
int t,i;
cin>>t;
for(i=0;i<t;i++)
{
	r.x1=r.x2=r.y1=r.y2=0;
	cin>>r1.x1>>r1.y1>>r1.x2>>r1.y2;
	cin>>r2.x1>>r2.y1>>r2.x2>>r2.y2;
	if(r1.x1<r2.x1)
	{
		if(r1.x2>r2.x1)
		{
			r.x1=r1.x2;
			r.x2=r2.x1;
		}
	}
	else
	{
		if(r2.x2>r1.x1)
		{
			r.x1=r2.x2;
			r.x2=r1.x1;
		}
	}
	//Y
	if(r1.y1<r2.y1)
	{
		if(r1.y2>r2.y1)
		{
			r.y1=r1.y2;
			r.y2=r2.y1;
		}
	}
	else
	{
		if(r2.y2>r1.y1)
		{
			r.y1=r2.y2;
			r.y2=r1.y1;
		}
	}
	//Output
	if(r.x1+r.x2+r.y1+r.y2==0)
		cout<<"No Overlap";
	else
		cout<<r.x2<<" "<<r.y2<<" "<<r.x1<<" "<<r.y1;
	cout<<endl;
}
return 0;
}
